article.description: — Jordan Ivy-Curry had a career-high 27 points as UTSA beat Denver 78-64 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Ivy-Curry scores 27 to carry UTSA over Denver 78-64
article.linkText: Ivy-Curry scores 27 to carry UTSA over Denver 78-64
article.story: SAN ANTONIO -- — Jordan Ivy-Curry had a career-high 27 points as UTSA beat Denver 78-64 on Tuesday night. Jacob Germany had 17 points for UTSA (2-2). Dhieu Deing added 11 points. Jordan Johnson had 19 points for the Pioneers (2-2).
